The evidence with the title 'High-risk pools for uninsurable individuals | the Henry J. Kaiser ... ' says Feb 22, 2017  ... For more than 35 years , many states operated high-risk pool programs to offer non - group health coverage to uninsurable residents. ... Private health insurance pools risks so that premiums paid by most enrollees , who have low claims costs , help pay claims for the small share of enrollees with high costs . 
